          <Icon
            name="heroicons-outline:template"
            class="flex items-center flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 mx-2 my-2 text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400"
          />

          <h4 class="text-f-lg font-display font-semibold">No templates</h4>
        </div>
        <p>
          I never use templates. Your website will be carefully crafted from
          scratch, just for you. That includes every small element. I don't use
          bootstrap or any other framework templates.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <Icon
            name="icon-park-outline:optimize"
            class="flex items-center flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 mx-2 my-2 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400"
          />

          <h4 class="text-f-lg font-display font-semibold">Optimization</h4>
        </div>
        <p>
          When optimizing a website for performance, there are three primary
          types of front end optimization techniques.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-decimal">
          <li>Techniques that reduce the number of requests.</li>
          <li>Techniques that reduce the overall size of the content.</li>
          <li>
            Practices that promote parallelization (i.e. simultaneous download
            of assets).
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          By structuring the HTML properly, optimizing images, minifying CSS and
          JavaScript, your website will be lightening fast.
        </p>
        <div>
          You can check the performance audits of this website below.
          <ul class="mt-4 list-inside list-decimal">
            <li>
              <Link
                href="/data/GTmetrix-report-weboreviews.com-20221113T043524-unorHqJA.pdf"
                target="_blank">GTmetrix Analysis (2022-11-13)</Link
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <Link
                href="/data/weboreviews.com_2022-11-13_17-55-04.report-desktop.html"
                target="_blank"
                >Lighthouse - desktop device (2022-11-13)
              </Link>
            </li>
            <li>
              <Link
                href="/data/weboreviews.com_2022-11-13_17-57-50.report-mobile.html"
                target="_blank"
                >Lighthouse - mobile device (2022-11-13)
              </Link>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

